00:00:29.435 --> 00:00:32.569
Condividerà con noi la sua visione

00:00:32.569 --> 00:00:34.619
dell'India urbana.

00:00:34.909 --> 00:00:36.659
TED Talks India New Thoughts

00:00:36.659 --> 00:00:38.439
dà il benvenuto al Dr. Gautam Bhan.

00:00:38.469 --> 00:00:40.089
Dr. Gautam Bhan, prego.

00:00:40.639 --> 00:00:48.769
(Applausi)

00:00:51.039 --> 00:00:52.332
In questo paese,

00:00:52.332 --> 00:00:53.625
